High School: Graduated from Redlands East Valley HS in 2011…was named to the CIF all-Inland Division and first team all-Citrus Belt League as a senior… tallied 31 tackles as a senior while helping the team to an 8-3 record…the Wildcats won CBL titles his final two seasons…had six interceptions as a senior and 14 during his career to set school records…picked off three passes against Redlands…also earned all-CBL honors in track. Personal: Has yet to declare a major...parents are Robert Armstrong and Naomi Rodriguez.}
